sub_title: Sustainable performance and business success consultant | Circular & Sharing economy Expert | Co-Founder CAT-scan
summary:
In order to ensure a liveable future, we must re-shape our mindset and find a balance between our society, planet and economy. Decoupling economic growth with ecological footprint is about creating business models and creating business success in a sustainable manner. We work with tools like the circular economy, sharing economy, SDG's, the Doughnut Economics, technologies to help companies succeed as a sustainable business.

Having worked with all kinds of stakeholders; companies, governments and municipalities, knowledge institutions, NGO's etc., I have recognized the value of bringing the ecosystem together and evolving in a holistic and collaborative manner. 

There is no society without our planet. And there is no economy without our society.
